{"article_id":"dtyGknH3cI4Th0TT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Republicans are n't waiting for Brett Kavanaugh 's main accuser to have her say .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"With a generational conservative goal of a Supreme Court majority in sight ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Senate GOP leaders are sketching a voting timetable","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that could see him confirmed within days","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"even as they brace for a crucial hearing on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"on which the judge 's fate rests .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"In another bold move , the party hired a female prosecutor","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"experienced in sex crime cases","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"to question Kavanaugh and Christine Blasey Ford ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"who accuses him of sexually assaulting her","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"when they were teenagers in the 1980s .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Kavanaugh denies all the allegations against him .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"The GOP power play could see the Senate Judiciary Committee vote on Kavanaugh 's nomination as soon as Friday , procedural votes at the weekend and a final Senate decision by early next week ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"assuming","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"there are no more complications .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"The choice of veteran attorney Rachel Mitchell","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"to ask the questions","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"represents a stiff challenge to Ford ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"who will be stepping into a global spotlight","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to tell her story at a quintessential moment of American history .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"She had hoped to be fielding the less-focused queries of a male-only bench of Republican senators .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"The GOP attempt","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"to restore Kavanaugh 's momentum","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"came amid tangible impatience in the party over his stalled progress ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"and as President Donald Trump 's frustration erupted in a stunning personal attack on the judge 's accusers ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"charging","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"their claims were just a Democratic `` C-O-N . ''","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"`` It 's a very dangerous game for our country , ''","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Trump said Tuesday ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"that a Deborah Ramirez , a second woman","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"who came forward with a complaint about Kavanaugh","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"while he was at Yale University ,","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"had `` nothing ''","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"and saying","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"she was `` messed up '' and `` drunk '' at the time of the alleged incident .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"And in a late-night tweet Tuesday , Trump warned","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"`` the Democrats are playing a high level CON GAME in their vicious effort","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"to destroy a fine person .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"It is called the politics of destruction .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"Behind the scene the Dems are laughing .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Pray for Brett Kavanaugh and his family ! ''","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"The Republican gambit also left Democrats seeking new ways","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"to slow Kavanaugh 's progress amid speculation","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that new allegations could emerge","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"to weaken his candidacy","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"-- a possibility","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that the GOP seemed to be trying to forestall","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"by driving forward swiftly in the confirmation process .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"But it also appeared to risk inflaming the toxic politics around the nomination","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and falling foul of the changed environment around allegations of sexual misconduct","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"involving powerful men","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"as the # MeToo movement changes politics , the media , business and Hollywood .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"The fact","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that anyone with power in Washington is living on their nerves","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"as the confirmation fight intensifies","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"also underscores the massive stakes","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Kavanaugh 's nomination represents with midterms less than six weeks away .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Women voters already favor Democrats over Republicans ahead of November 's elections ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"so the party can ill afford to seen as further traumatizing Ford .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"`` Rush Limbaugh to Republicans :","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"'You can kiss the MIDTERMS goodbye","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"if you do n't get highly qualified Kavanaugh approved . ' ''","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"I have no doubt","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"that ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"if the attack on Dr. Ford was as bad","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"as she says ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"charges would have been immediately filed with local Law Enforcement Authorities by either her or her loving parents .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"I ask","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"that she bring those filings forward","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"so that we can learn date , time , and place !","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"September 21 , 2018","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Republicans appeared encouraged Tuesday by Kavanaugh 's Fox News appearance with his wife ,","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"in which he vehemently denied any sexual wrongdoing","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"and vowed","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"that his nomination would not be driven out of the confirmation fight by a `` false allegation . ''","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"With some senators predicting procedural votes in the Senate on the nomination at the weekend ,","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Judiciary Chairman Chuck Grassley , R-Iowa , scheduled a vote in his committee on Friday in the hope","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"that Republicans on the panel will be ready to move forward","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"after hearing from Ford .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"Democrats reacted with fury to Grassley 's move ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"that it prejudged the outcome of Thursday 's hearing","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"and showed","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Republicans did n't want a fair process","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"and had no interest","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"in finding the truth .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"`` For Republicans to schedule a Friday vote on Brett Kavanaugh today , two days before Dr. Blasey Ford has had a chance","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"to tell her story ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"is outrageous , ''","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"said California Sen. Dianne Feinstein , the ranking Democrat on the committee .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"`` First Republicans demanded","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"Dr. Blasey Ford testify immediately .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"Now Republicans do n't even need to hear her","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"before they move ahead with a vote , ''","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Another Democrat , Sen Jeff Merkley of Oregon , complained","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"that Republicans were conducting a `` jammed through , unfair process '' on a lifetime Supreme Court appointment .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"`` The President is attacking the victims .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"That is just horrific in this day and age .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"I guess","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that is what we have come to expect from this individual in the Oval Office , ''","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Merkley said on CNN 's `` The Situation Room with Wolf Blitzer . ''","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"And Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , of New York , jabbed GOP Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , in unusually personal terms ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"he owed Ford an apology","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"for labeling her allegations as a `` smear job . ''","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"But McConnell , of Kentucky , indicated","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"that he believes","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that nothing","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"that happens on Thursday","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"will keep Kavanaugh from the court .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"`` We 're going to be moving forward ,","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"I 'm confident","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"we 're going to win .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"I 'm confident ...","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"he will be confirmed in the very near future . ''","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"McConnell told reporters .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"despite laying the groundwork for a vote ,","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"Republican leaders still can not count on holding their majority .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"If two Republicans defect","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"and all the Democrats vote against Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"his nomination is doomed .","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"The two most likely GOP senators","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"to flip ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Sens . Susan Collins of Maine and Lisa Murkowski of Alaska , are under intense political pressure from both sides of the aisle .","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"Murkowski appeared to hint at daylight with the leadership of her party Tuesday ,","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"suggesting","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"that Ramirez ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"whose allegations broke in a story in The New Yorker over the weekend ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"should be brought into the congressional process .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"Asked whether an FBI investigation would help ,","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"a vetting step","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"rejected by the committee and the White House ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Murkowski answered :","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"`` It would sure clear up all the questions ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"would n't it ? ''","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"Collins refused to tip her hand ,","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"but did dismiss Democratic calls","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"to postpone the Thursday 's hotly anticipated committee proceedings ,","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"the hearing this week is very important . ''","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"CORRECTION :","depth":5},{"id":149,"text":"This story has been updated","depth":6},{"id":150,"text":"to reflect the correct date of President Donald Trump 's tweet .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":301,"left":0,"right":300,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":300,"left":225,"right":299,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":171,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":162,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":156,"right":161,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":1,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":2,"right":154,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":152,"right":153,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":